    "attributes": {
        "product_description": {
            "value": "Does your child love Star Wars and creating artwork? The officially licensed Disney sticker set comes with 4 sheets of stickers, all featuring characters from the hit movie franchise: BB8, C3P0, Fett, Luke, Han Solo, and more.\r\n\r\nKids can practice learning the alphabet with this A-Z sticker set - a different character from the movie franchise represents each letter. Fun and educational stickers are an excellent option for kids to add to their homework and school art projects. Stationery stickers can encourage extra creativity and imagination!\r\n\r\nAll 4 sticker sheets included are safe for children ages 3 and up with adult supervision. The durable and vibrant stickers are sure to add a fun flair to any art project. Make sure to grab this set of stickers for your little Star Wars fan!",
